      "dimensions": 1,
      "description": "step - This parameter sets how many frames pass before the  grabs one into cache. A Sample Step of 1 will grab each consecutive frame, a Sample Step of 2 will grab every other frame, and so on.\t\nWhen Prefilling you would normally setup the inputs to the Texture 3D node in some way that is tied to $F. Such as a Movie File In  where set the Specify Index parameter to $F - 1 (since 0 is the first frame). Or a Noise  that is changing it's translation based on $F. If Step Size is 3, it would cook frame 1, 4, 7 etc.",
      "tooltip": "",
      "help": "",
      "units": "",
